              span Call Now
          
        .letter-frame

          .entry
            p Hi, my name is #[span(id='yourName')] and I am a California resident, calling from #[span(id='yourCity')]. My zip code is #[span(id='yourZip')]. 
            p I am extremely concerned about the lack of leadership that Senator Harris has shown on climate change. I understand that there are many important causes she can choose from to focus on, and I am pleading with her to make this issue her priority. 
            p Senator Harris can fill the void left by our President, and like the state of California she can become a global leader to protect our climate. I would like her to at least make a public statement, and introduce resolutions in the Senate. I will watch her actions and hold her accountable if she does not take serious action. I would like a response to my call. Thank you!


